Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:29.58,Main,One particular random marine,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.99,Main,One particular random marine,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... please tell me this isn't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:39.32,Main,One particular random marine,0000,0000,0000,,The fortress of Justice, the Navy's base,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:43.66,Main,One particular random marine,0000,0000,0000,,which has protected the oceans of the world for centuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:46.62,Main,One particular random marine,0000,0000,0000,,How could it end up like this?!
