Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:01.24,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,has stolen Whitebeard's powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:04.72,Main,Blackbeard,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, all you people of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:08.35,Main,Blackbeard,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me, and my power!
