Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:16:00.73,Flashbacks,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I have already decided to protect this man, even if it costs me my life!{End copy-paste from 486}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.98,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let him die...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:33.55,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I die myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:36.69,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let Luffy-kun die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.60,Main,Gendo Ikari,0000,0000,0000,,What an absurd claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.16,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:08.21,Main,Crocodile,0000,0000,0000,,Someone catch him, and get him on a ship already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.29,Main,Pirates,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:11.21,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:14.83,Main,Crocodile,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to protect something, then you should do it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:18.72,Main,Crocodile,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let these guys keep doing whatever they want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.22,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.92,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over... {Go die.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:28.23,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry for getting carried away, everyone. {THAT'S NOT WHAT YOU NEED TO APOLOGIZE FOR! APOLOGIZE FOR YOUR CONTINUED STUPID COMIC RELIEF FILLER THAT ISN'T EVEN REMOTELY FUNNY AND TOTALLY RUINS THE MOOD INSTEAD, YOU EFFING DOUCHE!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:31.19,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,The legend of Captain Buggy is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:34.46,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your support up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.60,Main,Pirates,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:44.66,Main,Pirates,0000,0000,0000,,He's not falling back down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:47.55,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.50,Main,Annoying retards,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:53.00,Main,Annoying retards,0000,0000,0000,,You saved Straw Hat and Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.05,Main,Annoying retards,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:18:00.01,Main,Annoying retards,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy... You just made it look like you were running away,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:04.19,Main,Annoying retards,0000,0000,0000,,so that you could save your fellow escapee, Straw Hat, in his time of need!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.74,Main,Annoying retards,0000,0000,0000,,How noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:10.61,Main,Annoying retards,0000,0000,0000,,Your nobility is blinding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:14.03,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,They're acting weird again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.95,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe and Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:24.57,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell did you end up flying into the sky, covered in blood like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:26.45,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it sure is hot here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:31.42,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Magma!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:37.00,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Red Nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.43,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,You saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:41.14,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno what just happened, but I wasn't {\i1}trying{\i0} to save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:46.64,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I let Luffy-kun get another grave injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.56,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,We must treat his wounds immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:52.64,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up!  I'm the one who needs help, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:54.85,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we can treat him up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:57.51,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!  Who're you calling Red Nose?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:00.95,Main,Gendo Ikari,0000,0000,0000,,At the last possible moment, another one gets in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:24.23,Main,Gendo Ikari,0000,0000,0000,,All the pests have gathered together...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:28.05,Main,Gendo Ikari,0000,0000,0000,,Do you all wish to die for that Straw Hat's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:35.52,Main,Vista,0000,0000,0000,,We've all seen his bottomless tenacity and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:39.99,Main,Fossa,0000,0000,0000,,He's the man Ace protected, and the Old Man respected him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:44.03,Main,Izou,0000,0000,0000,,It is our duty to send him on to the new era!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:48.66,Main,Gendo Ikari,0000,0000,0000,,Every last one of you are fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:01.68,Main,Gendo Ikari,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:03.84,Main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Akainu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:08.39,Main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,The great danger you see in that boy you're trying to kill right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:13.44,Main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,and the great potential we see in the one we're attempting to rescue...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.73,Main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they the same thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:19.73,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you got me involved again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.84,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,You listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:23.80,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, J-Jinbe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:28.27,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,You're unconscious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:31.16,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where should I go now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.65,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:37.70,Main,Crocodile,0000,0000,0000,,Whether he's alive or dead, it's like he's in Hell anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:41.72,Main,Crocodile,0000,0000,0000,,So let's just leave him alive and let him suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:46.72,Main,Gendo Ikari,0000,0000,0000,,I guess nothing I say will stop you at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:49.49,Main,Gendo Ikari,0000,0000,0000,,Do your worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:04.90,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:08.37,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Sengoku and Blackbeard are over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:18.21,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,And Akainu and the Commanders are over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:28.23,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,The battle will never end!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:31.35,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy!  Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.39,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:36.31,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:04.09,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!  We've reached a point clear of the ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:06.26,Main,Law,0000,0000,0000,,Take us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:17.27,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.35,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,A ship emerged from the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:21.75,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,That's a submarine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:23.94,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Another enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:25.95,Main,Pirate,0000,0000,0000,,Whose ship is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:29.86,Main,Law,0000,0000,0000,,Bring Straw-Hatter over here! {So yeah, I've completely ignored Law's speech-quirk earlier as I couldn't think of a decent way to adapt it and thought "Straw Hat-ya" sounded utterly retarded, but seeing how they actually POINT IT OUT here, I suppose I can't really do that any more... So I went with the same translation that Stephen did.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:36.12,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,"Straw-Hatter"?  That sure is a weird way of addressing a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:38.16,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:41.41,Main,Law,0000,0000,0000,,Straw-Hatter and I will probably end up as enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:42.63,Main,Law,0000,0000,0000,,but I have nothing against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.39,0:22:46.09,Main,Law,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be no fun to have him die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:49.18,Main,Law,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So I'm gonna take him away from this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:50.89,Main,Law,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let me take care of him for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:52.43,Main,Buggy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:00.89,Main,Law,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.03,0:23:22.58,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy's fierce assault doesn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:28.29,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,On the battlefield, where the meaningless battle drags on, one man is overwhelmed by sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:32.02,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And that sadness gives birth to the great power known as courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:34.35,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and causes the very fate of the world to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:35.53,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:36.85,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,A Desperate Cry
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:39.76,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,A Moment of Courage that Changes Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:41.79,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
